summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6085 for the improvement of West Henderson Street from 45th Avenue Southwest to California by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 83777, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
